<title type="html"><![CDATA[7/21(Thu) The Pros and Cons of Marriage/ The Secrets of Learning a New Language (Host: Maggie)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=635&amp;p=660#p660"><![CDATA[
The Pros and Cons of Marriage/ The Secrets of Learning a New Language (Host: Maggie)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40: Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />Session 1: The Pros and Cons of Marriage<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NSD2WW8xieY">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NSD2WW8xieY</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1. Do you think the marriage system is the most perfect system for <br />human beings?<br />2. Given the same chance, would you choose the same outcome?<br />3. Young people don't like getting married, Do you agree?<br />4. What is your advice on marriage? Do you have any good advice?<br /><br /><br /><br />Session 2: The Secrets of Learning a New Language<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o_XVt5rdpFY">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=o_XVt5rdpFY</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><br />Questions:<br /><br />1. How may languages do you speak? including dialects包括方言。<br />Do you think it's fun to learn a new language ?<br />2.Can you teach us one or two words, about different countries  language ?for instance：[ thank you,good bye, how are you? l love you,,,,etcetera. ]<br />3.  For how long you did spend your time for the new language?<br />4. Having casualy conversations with others. please feel free to share your opinion with others.<br /><br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38674">Louie Wang</a> — Sat Jul 16, 2022 10:23 am</p><hr />
